        <h2>Diet Plan</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Breakfast:</strong> Oatmeal with flaxseeds, nuts, and honey.</li>
            <li><strong>Lunch:</strong> Grilled chicken with brown rice and roasted vegetables.</li>
            <li><strong>Snacks:</strong> Low-fat yogurt with granola and mixed berries.</li>
            <li><strong>Dinner:</strong> Stir-fried tofu with quinoa and steamed broccoli.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Gym Routine</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Strength training (moderate resistance) 4-5 times a week.</li>
            <li>Cardio (walking, swimming) 3-4 times a week.</li>
            <li>Mobility and flexibility exercises (yoga, stretching) after workouts.</li>
        </ul>
